        <p>More information on the Essential<sup>Â®</sup> ASP.NET Core Gantt Chart can be found in this <a target="_blank" href="https://ej2.syncfusion.com/aspnetcore/documentation/gantt/managing-tasks/editing-tasks#dialog-editing">documentation section</a>.</p>
</div>
